Class LinqQuery<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linq4android.collections.LinqQuery<T>

    public class LinqQuery<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<T>
    Provides capabilities of query on java.util.Iterable<T> or an array with chainable methods
